  "instructions": [
    "prepare the ingredients: peel and mince the ginger, garlic and green chili.",
    "mix the cocoa powder and black sesame oil together in a bowl.",
    "submerge the black pudding in the cocoa powder mixture and coat evenly.",
    "place the coated black pudding on the bamboo skewers.",
    "place the sushi vinegar rice on the skewers around the black pudding.",
    "season the rice with soy sauce, mirin, rice vinegar and sugar.",
    "place the skewers in the sous-vide machine and cook at 85°C for 1 hour.",
    "grill the skewers over a robata-grill for 2 minutes on each side.",
    "cut the skewers into bite-sized pieces and serve with yuzu juice.",
    "serve with lemon wedges on the side."
